---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Products — Premium Aluminium Alloy and Primary Ingots | Egypt Alumin" 
  description="Explore our three core product lines engineered for European manufacturing: A7 primary aluminium ingots, ADC12 die-casting alloys, and high-performance Al-Si silicon-alloys. All CBAM-ready and certified to EN standards."
  lang="en"
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="container">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/en/">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">Products</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="product-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="product-hero-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
        <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Egypt Alumin Catalogue</span>
          <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Premium Aluminium Ingots & Alloys</h1>
          <p class="product-hero-lead" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">
            Engineered to EN standards. CBAM-ready with verified Scope 1 & 2 emissions data.
            Supplying automotive foundries, extruders, and rolling mills across Germany, Italy, France, and the UK.
          </p>
          <div class="product-hero-badges" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <span>ISO 9001 Certified</span>
            <span>REACH Compliant</span>
            <span>CBAM Ready</span>
            <span>Guaranteed Traceability</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="products-section" style="background: var(--white); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="product-grid">

        <!-- Card 1: A7 -->
        <article class="product-card-modern">
          <div class="product-img-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/products/2.2-a7-aluminium-ingot-bundle-steel-strapped-palletised.webp" alt="A7 Ingot" class="product-img-asset" />
            <div class="product-img-overlay">
              <span class="product-img-label">A7 Primary Aluminium Ingot · 25 kg</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-body">
            <span class="product-tag">EN 576 · P1020A · GB/T 1196</span>
            <h3 class="product-title" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">A7 Primary Aluminium Ingot</h3>
            <div class="product-specs" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              <span>Al ≥ 99.7%</span>
              <span>25 kg ingot</span>
              <span>P1020A grade</span>
            </div>
            <p class="product-desc" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">The foundational raw material for aluminium processing — high purity, minimal impurities, ready for remelting and further fabrication into rolling slab, extrusion log, and wire rod.</p>
            <a href="/en/products/a7-primary-aluminium-ingot/" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; text-align: center; justify-content: center;">
              View Technical Specs
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 2: ADC12 -->
        <article class="product-card-modern">
          <div class="product-img-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/products/2.3-adc12-die-casting-aluminium-alloy-ingot-en-ac-46000.webp" alt="ADC12 Alloy" class="product-img-asset" />
            <div class="product-img-overlay">
              <span class="product-img-label">ADC12 Die-Casting Ingot · 20 kg</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-body">
            <span class="product-tag">EN AC-46000 · JIS H 5302</span>
            <h3 class="product-title" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">ADC12 Die-Casting Alloy</h3>
            <div class="product-specs" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              <span>Si 9.6–12%</span>
              <span>20 kg ingot</span>
              <span>AlSi9Cu3(Fe)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="product-desc" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">The industry-standard die-casting alloy for thin-walled, complex castings at scale — stable mechanical properties, excellent castability, and high fluidity for thin geometries.</p>
            <a href="/en/products/adc12-die-casting-alloy/" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; text-align: center; justify-content: center;">
              View Technical Specs
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 3: AlSi -->
        <article class="product-card-modern">
          <div class="product-img-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/products/2.4-aluminium-silicon-alloy-ingot-en-1706-precision-casting.webp" alt="AL-Si Alloy" class="product-img-asset" />
            <div class="product-img-overlay">
              <span class="product-img-label">AL-Si Alloy Ingot · 20 kg</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-body">
            <span class="product-tag">EN 1706 · GB/T 1173</span>
            <h3 class="product-title" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">AL-Si Aluminium-Silicon Alloy</h3>
            <div class="product-specs" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              <span>Al ≥ 99.7% + Si</span>
              <span>20 kg ingot</span>
              <span>AC-4xxxx series</span>
            </div>
            <p class="product-desc" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Precision-formulated aluminium-silicon alloys with superior fluidity and low copper content (≤ 0.05%) — engineered for EV battery trays, chassis castings, and safety-critical components.</p>
            <a href="/en/products/aluminium-silicon-alloy-ingot/" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; text-align: center; justify-content: center;">
              View Technical Specs
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CATALOGUE CTA
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="cbam" aria-labelledby="cat-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cbam-inner" style="grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr; align-items: center;">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Full Technical Documentation</span>
          <h2 id="cat-heading">Download Our Comprehensive Product Catalogue</h2>
          <p>
            Get full chemical composition ranges, mechanical properties across tempers, casting guidelines,
            and logistics packaging profiles in our unified PDF catalogue. Aligned with European buying offices.
          </p>
          <a href="/assets/product-catalogue.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">
            Download Catalogue PDF
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M19 12l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
          <h4 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif; color:var(--amber); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Included Technical Data:</h4>
          <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.75rem; font-size:0.9rem;">
            <li>✓ Element-by-element impurity tolerances</li>
            <li>✓ Mechanical metrics (Yield, Tensile, Brinell)</li>
            <li>✓ Microstructure modification details (Sr/Na)</li>
            <li>✓ CBAM reporting template specifications</li>
            <li>✓ EU customs EORI and documentation checklist</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       FINAL CTA
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Direct European Sales Office</span>
      <h2>Discuss your custom requirements with Noel</h2>
      <p>Whether you need a specific composition window, particular packaging bundles, or a sample shipment for trial heats, speak directly with our European partner in Ireland.</p>
      <div class="final-cta-actions">
        <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:+353871187806" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Noel: +353 87 118 7806</a>
      </div>
      <p class="final-cta-direct">
        Direct Email: <a href="mailto:noel@egyptalumin.com">noel@egyptalumin.com</a> · WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/353871187806">Direct Chat</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .product-img-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--navy);
  }
  .product-img-asset {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.85;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease, opacity 0.5s ease;
  }
  .product-card-modern:hover .product-img-asset {
    transform: scale(1.06);
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .product-img-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 0%, transparent 60%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .product-card-modern {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  .product-card-modern:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--teal);
  }
</style>
